<br>
It is a very nice AA skill, and maybe it shows how weak some other class AA skills are, but by no means should it be nerf'd just so that Wizard class AA can suck as bad as ours, or any other class.<br>
<br>
Can only speak for my server ( TM ), but I see very little change with the introduction of MB.  Our local MB team has only got Sev 1 out of the last 5 or 6 kills ( don't know about the others, ) but if the MB team does not get them, they still won't be up that long.  Everything dies so quickly on our server, that most guilds will jump at the opportunity to kill anything.<br>
<br>
The only other 'issue' I see people griping about is Risk vs. Reward.  People have tried to explain that there is 'risk' for a MB team; you either agree or don't.<br>
