Again, Glatius2, you seem to only be upset about the fact that the mob is dying fast.  You say specifically that is the problem.  You don't seem to mind that the mob is dying at the hands of 6 people, but that it's dying in a small amount of time.  I don't see the logic behind this.  What's the difference?  My 56 warrior can annihilate crushbone at a faster and more consistant rate than my 52 wizard.  That doesn't mean a thing.  It's still 1 person trivializing content that is designed for less powerful or a larger number of people.<br>
